5$ $(15)$. We end by exploring the impact of two reionization feedback\nscenarios, in which we suppress the gas content of galaxies with\n$T_{\\mathrm{vir}}<20000\\mathrm{K}$ and $v_{c}<30\\mathrm{kms^{-1}}$ residing in\nionized regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 May 2023 16:51:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-16"}
