oupling behaviors of the photosensitive hydrogel, and then\nproviding guidelines for the application of photoisomerization hydrogel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 May 2023 06:05:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-16"}
