handed and right-handed polarized waves corresponds to the\nAlfv\\'en ion cyclotron mode wave and the fast-magnetosonic whistler mode wave,\nrespectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 May 2023 08:08:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-16"}
