 of $n$ numbers requires $\\Omega(n)$ parallel time and the problem can be\nsolved in $O(n\\log n)$ parallel time in expectation and whp in standard\npopulation protocols. Finally, we show $O(\\log^4 n)$ parallel time median\ncomputation in selective population protocols.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 May 2023 09:01:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-16"}
