ns about using such data for LLM-involved evaluation in academic\ndevelopment. To deal with it, we propose a novel index associated with a\ndataset that roughly decides the feasibility of using such data for\nLLM-involved evaluation. Extensive empirical studies are tagged to support the\naforementioned claims.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 May 2023 15:44:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 May 2023 06:56:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 25 May 2023 05:01:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-26"}
